<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:14:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>下半年预测疲弱后，开云集团股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/kering-shares-sink-after-weak-h2-forecast-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四早盘，法国奢侈品集团古驰（Gucci）母公司开云集团（Kering）的股价大幅下跌，此前这家法国奢侈品集团公布第二季度销售额降幅超出预期，并警告称，由于中国需求疲弱，下半年将出现疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:13:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/kering-shares-sink-after-weak-h2-forecast-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康因药品需求强劲而上调利润预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-lifts-full-year-outlook-upbeat-demand-therapies-2024-07-25/</link><description>英瑞制药商阿斯利康周四上调全年销售额和利润预期，因癌症、罕见病和心脏病药物需求强劲，第二季度营收超出分析师预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-lifts-full-year-outlook-upbeat-demand-therapies-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>上半年业绩疲软后，Stellantis 计划减产、降价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-misses-forecasts-with-h1-drop-revenue-operating-income-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，全球第四大汽车制造商 Stellantis 承诺采取措施解决北美和其他地区的问题，包括削减产量和价格，此前这家全球第四大汽车制造商的上半年业绩低于预期，导致其股价下跌 10%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-misses-forecasts-with-h1-drop-revenue-operating-income-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>联合利华出售 Truliva 股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unilever-sells-stake-truliva-2024-07-25/</link><description>联合利华周四表示，已出售其在沁源集团（又名 Truliva）的股份，但未透露出售的财务条款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:26:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unilever-sells-stake-truliva-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于主流芯片市场疲软达到第三季度预期，Besi 股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaking-parts-supplier-besi-posts-better-than-expected-q2-orders-2024-07-25/</link><description>荷兰芯片制造零部件供应商BE半导体工业公司（Besi）周四预测第三季度销售额持平，低于预期，受到主流组装市场（尤其是中国）增长疲软的打击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:56:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaking-parts-supplier-besi-posts-better-than-expected-q2-orders-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>市场分析师对中国意外降息的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/market-analysts-react-surprise-rate-cut-china-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国周四非周期削减银行融资成本，令金融市场感到意外。在宣布将一年期中期贷款便利 (MLF) 下调 20 个基点后，股市下跌，债券上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/market-analysts-react-surprise-rate-cut-china-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行再次以较低利率放贷，令人意外</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-surprises-by-lending-again-lower-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国央行周四以极低的利率进行了计划外贷款操作，本周第二次令市场感到意外，这表明当局正试图提供更大规模的货币刺激措施以支撑经济。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:01:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-surprises-by-lending-again-lower-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风期间货轮在台湾海域沉没 九名船员失踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/freighter-sinks-off-taiwan-during-typhoon-nine-crew-missing-2024-07-25/</link><description>台湾消防部门周四表示，一艘悬挂坦桑尼亚国旗、载有九名缅甸国民的货轮在台风期间在南部港口城市高雄海岸沉没，船员尚未做出回应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/freighter-sinks-off-taiwan-during-typhoon-nine-crew-missing-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>BASIC集团猛烈抨击气候变化和金融领域的“领导力无效”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/basic-bloc-slams-leadership-void-climate-change-finance-2024-07-25/</link><description>巴西、南非、印度和中国组成的基础四国集团周三晚间表示，富裕国家在气候政治方面留下了“领导力真空”，必须提供数万亿美元来帮助发展中国家减少温室气体排放。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/basic-bloc-slams-leadership-void-climate-change-finance-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回大亨黎智英终止审判的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</link><description>香港一家法院周四驳回了法律团队对被监禁的民主人士黎智英结束国家安全审判的请求，称检察官似乎有足够的证据支持对他的所有三项指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>科技股动荡重创全球股市，日元飙升至 2-1/2 个月高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，由于全球科技股暴跌，投资者纷纷逃往债券、日元和瑞士法郎等传统避险资产，股市陷入了数万亿美元的混乱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国需求疲软和中东停火谈判而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于对全球最大原油进口国中国需求疲软的担忧以及对中东即将达成停火协议的预期克服了美国库存减少后前一交易日的涨幅，油价周四下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>套利交易平仓、风险情绪恶化，日元大幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-rises-carry-trades-unwind-risk-sentiment-takes-hit-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于日元套利交易平仓和风险偏好恶化，周四日元兑美元汇率升至 2-1/2 个月来的最高水平，并在下周日本央行 (BOJ) 会议之前兑其他货币攀升至数月高点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-rises-carry-trades-unwind-risk-sentiment-takes-hit-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风“盖美”在台湾海域击沉货轮，冲向中国沿海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，台风“嘉美”横扫台湾北部，造成三人死亡，引发洪水并沉没一艘货轮，然后向西穿过台湾海峡，抵达中国大陆，预计将带来更多暴雨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中资银行下调存款利率以缓解利润率挤压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国五家主要国有银行周四下调了存款利率，以缓解本周意外降低贷款基准以提振经济增长后对本已创纪录低位利润率的打击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>